Paul Heyman announces that Roman Reigns has removed himself from Draft eligibility because he is not returning in the immediate future

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d9dd997a-47d6-4199-b76e-b037b88f25b6/20240426_170853.jpg)

NXT is hosting a real life draft party. With fans included.

