![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0b5dabab-c963-47d1-b805-4874887e13e1/20240426_170849.jpg)

The Draft War Rooms, featuring JBL, D-Von, Bubba Ray and Teddy Long

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ad584a5e-3352-4314-a853-0c191570404a/20240426_171549.jpg)

*   ## **_CODY RHODES AND AJ STYLES WWE CHAMPIONSHIP CONTRACT SIGNING_**
    

AJ says what he did to LA Knight was personal but he doesn’t have been with Cody. He respects his father, the American Dream. He’s wrestled Dream before.

Cody says he respects that AJ is familiar with the Rhodes family but when he puts ‘Cody' in front of the RHODES. It stops being a Dream match and becomes a “must win”.

AJ says it’s a shame that he has to take the WWE Title from Cody so soon after he won it.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9ad7372e-7f26-4a5f-90d9-116fd6221d72/Screenshot_20240426-171921_Chrome.jpg)

Triple H interrupted Cody's entrance and asks him to reveal the first few draft picks for Round 1

Bianca Belair to Smackdown

Jey Uso to RAW

Carmello Hayes to Smackdown

Seth Rollins to Raw

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f0107d2d-3de4-45bb-b558-f3f147c9583c/20240426_172457.jpg)

Carmelo Hayes comes out and challenges the WWE Champion Cody Rhodes for a match tonight!!!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b95205d5-39ea-475d-b6ee-7776a9b9270f/Screenshot_20240426-173004_Chrome.jpg)

*   ## **_REY MYSTERIO AND DRAGON LEE DEF. ANGEL AND HUMBERTO GARZA_**
    

LWO takes the win after a pretty fast nothing match. Santos Escobar and Electra Lopez come out afterwards. He reveals that he did not attack Dragon Lee.

Electra Lopez reveals she found the security footage from the night Dragon Lee got attacked. It was CARLITO!!!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2b0ce531-8b60-4599-a9f5-1bb7302e4ccb/20240426_174340.jpg)

*   ## **_BRON BREAKKER DEF. CEDRIC ALEXANDER IN 15 SECONDS_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/25ea0803-99d5-471e-8fc3-a568f03dbf48/20240426_174651.jpg)

Nick Aldis announces Tiffany Stratton vs Naomi for a shot at Bayley's WWE Women's Championship

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/859b9117-989b-4303-95a0-76279d78e07f/20240426_175052.jpg)

Torrie Wilson and Michelle McCool are out to pick the 2nd Round of Draft Picks.

Randy Orton to Smackdown

Bron Breakker to RAW

Nia Jax to Smackdown

Liv Morgan to RAW

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/80d0a7b6-0667-46fb-8c8e-3954655e779f/20240426_175054.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cb2bca97-c3c5-4651-bbf8-0f56a446c36d/20240426_175559.jpg)

Solo arrives and asks Heyman if the Bloodline got drafted.

"You're adding new members to the Bloodline which means nobody knows what to expect when they draft the group."

Tama Tonga shows up but both Tama and Solo are quickly attacked by Kevin Owens.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b6e2eece-75b7-4dd5-9d8a-e74dd192f97e/20240426_180145.jpg)

Bianca is out and she confirms her and Jade will challenge Kairi Sane and Asuka for the Women’s Tag Team Championships at Backlash.

She’s confronted by the Kabuki Warriors and quickly saved by Jade.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e3d057b9-f14c-482a-87bd-9a870a105bc8/20240426_180440.jpg)

Kevin Owens brawls Tama Tonga out right in between the Women’s Tag Team Championship segment. Owens gets jumped by Solo but he’s saved by Randy Orton.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/78d707de-5b3b-483d-a05b-98f76887376b/20240426_181119.jpg)

The Dudley Boyz are out to do ROUND 3 of the WWE Draft

LA Knight to Smackdown

Ricochet to RAW

The Bloodline(Solo, Paul and Tama) to Smackdown

Sheamus to RAW

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/feae6a5f-0204-4047-9655-0281e4d8baf9/20240426_182345.jpg)

*   ## **_NAOMI DEF. TIFFANY STRATTON BY DQ AFTER NIA JAX ATTACKED BAYLEY AND NAOMI_**
    

Tiffany rolled Bayley and Naomi into the ring after to hit a moonsault on them both at the same time.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/19a5ca94-64a4-4ad5-ab55-837b0c8549c5/20240426_183337.jpg)

JBL and Teddy Long come out to do ROUND 4 of the WWE Draft

AJ Styles to Smackdown

Alpha Academy to RAW

Andrade to Smackdown

Kiana James to RAW

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/91c3b6a8-ba86-4dc1-a977-3ffd86aae6e8/20240426_185806.jpg)

*   ## **_CODY RHODES DEF. CARMELO HAYES_**
    

What a weird match. I’m not sure what went wrong here. Not sure who to blame. But that was…. Off.

Show ends with AJ Styles facing down Cody Rhodes

